{"tid":1571104,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"國際文宣新方向建議","createTime":"2019-09-15T10:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T14:46:56.000Z","uid":19487,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3623f4470ab25c08536c91a4a7bbf0d48230d0c4","tid":1571104,"uid":19487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:29:05.000Z","msg":"美國其實有為數不少嘅左膠，由其係民主黨反侵個堆。<br />\n佢哋仍然主張對話與中國和解 因為中國對美國經濟有用，所有好多人其實係反人權法成立。<br />\n<br />\n大家文宣係咪應該話俾世界聽，<br />\n中共政權根本就唔會同你有君子交易，中共根本是唔會遵守合約同協議，所以你同佢傾好乜都仰廢嘅。<br />\n而且中國人會暗地裡偷呃拐騙其他國家嘅資源，華為已經係個好例子，將美國科技機密偷左一大堆。<br />\n<br />\n所以應該要話俾世界聽根本唔可以信中國政府同商家，而且更加要俾世界知道 同中國做生意，中國人會覺得係施捨俾你，你同中國做生意只會令中國人睇唔起你。"},{"pid":"34a63ee4f979deaa526afb4b94d7c596e449c81a","tid":1571104,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:30:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dee157c5e61cc14ef1a2a6e1926642b13fd4f470","tid":1571104,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:31:37.000Z","msg":"其實邊個國家都好<br />\n要輸出一個訊息：同中國合作你的利益會受損"},{"pid":"b4d5fef6b1a61f032cb43bb58133e37876c15e50","tid":1571104,"uid":19487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34a63ee4f979deaa526afb4b94d7c596e449c81a","tid":1571104,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:30:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:34:22.000Z","msg":"我地目標係令美國國民知道<br />\n而唔係想做國際仲裁"},{"pid":"cb2aad40b3c982ecb8c7f39d7a0832f2ad4c1c59","tid":1571104,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:34:31.000Z","msg":"你肯定美國左膠真係咁諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f063d47f576f806a4b3fd70f6132fbc60849a64a","tid":1571104,"uid":19487,"